Dialogue: 100,0:00:11.65,0:00:12.65,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文?\N{\rENG}Steven. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:13.02,0:00:13.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗨\N{\rENG}Hi. 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:13.73,0:00:15.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为什么我们不再准备钻头了?\N{\rENG}Why did we stop working on the drill? 
