Dialogue: 100,0:00:25.68,0:00:27.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}真的非常漂亮!\N{\rENG}It's beautiful! 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:27.71,0:00:30.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这一切都将被融合簇炸为虚无\N{\rENG}It's going to be blown to oblivion by the cluster
Dialogue: 100,0:00:30.55,0:00:31.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果我们不回去工作的话\N{\rENG}if we don't get back to work! 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:32.20,0:00:33.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}努力工作很重要 \N{\rENG}Working hard is important, 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:34.04,0:00:36.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但享受生活也很重要啊!\N{\rENG}but feeling good is important, too! 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:36.51,0:00:38.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你在说什么?!\N{\rENG}What are you talking about?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:38.82,0:00:40.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿-呲-!\N{\rENG}Hey--bzzzz! 
Dialogue: 100,0:00:41.08,0:00:42.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那是什么 一个C音?\N{\rENG}What is that, a--a "c"? 
