Dialogue: 100,0:03:26.57,0:03:27.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没错 史蒂文 月球\N{\rENG}Yeah, Steven, the moon. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:28.51,0:03:31.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}狮子 你给我们制造一个通向月球的超级传送吗?\N{\rENG}Lion, can you make us a special super warp to the moon? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:34.12,0:03:35.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}来吧 狮子!\N{\rENG}Come on, Lion! 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:35.26,0:03:37.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们必须做这个才能阻止融合簇!\N{\rENG}We got to do this to stop the cluster! 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:37.33,0:03:39.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果我们做不到 那就不不会有什么地球了!\N{\rENG}If we don't, there's gonna be no more earth! 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:39.57,0:03:41.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不会有朋友间的快乐时光!\N{\rENG}No more fun times with your pals! 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不会有狮子棒棒糖?\N{\rENG}No more Lion Lickers? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:43.75,0:03:44.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不会有懒觉了?\N{\rENG}No more naps? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:49.97,0:03:50.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看来是"懒觉"\N{\rENG}Guess it was "naps."
Dialogue: 100,0:03:58.47,0:04:00.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}挺酷的 对吧?!\N{\rENG}Pretty cool, right?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:07.02,0:04:10.29,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}上 狮子 上!\N{\rENG}Go, Lion, go! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:20.08,0:04:22.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}狮子! 你还好吗 伙计?\N{\rENG}Lion! Are you okay, bud? 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:24.06,0:04:26.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}让我从这个毛茸茸的怪胎里出来-呃! 嗷!\N{\rENG}Get me out of this furry freak--ugh! Ow! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:27.62,0:04:30.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 狮子 你为自己赢得了一周的懒觉!\N{\rENG}Aw, Lion, you've earned your naps for the week! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:32.71,0:04:33.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们做到了\N{\rENG}We made it. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:33.82,0:04:35.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这看起来不像是月球啊\N{\rENG}It doesn't look like the moon. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:36.24,0:04:38.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 看这里 我觉得这是个门!\N{\rENG}Hey, look over here. I think it's a door! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.68,0:04:41.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...对!\N{\rENG}Uh...Yep! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.40,0:04:43.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们在月球上!\N{\rENG}We on the moon! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:44.08,0:04:46.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶 求求你别把我们吸到太空中了!\N{\rENG}Amethyst, please don't blow us into space! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:48.03,0:04:48.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔!\N{\rENG}Whoa! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:53.43,0:04:54.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看看我!\N{\rENG}Look at me! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:54.64,0:04:56.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我是月球小子!\N{\rENG}I'm a moon boy! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哈哈! 好的 月球小子!\N{\rENG}Ha ha! All right, moon boy! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:02.06,0:05:03.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}月球小子 四重后空翻!\N{\rENG}Moon boy, quadruple backflip! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:04.44,0:05:05.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿!\N{\rENG}Hey! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:05.62,0:05:07.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我没什么就不能是月球小子?\N{\rENG}Why can't I be a moon boy? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:07.33,0:05:08.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们是宝石人\N{\rENG}We're gems. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.73,0:05:09.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们是太空种族\N{\rENG}We're a space-faring race
Dialogue: 100,0:05:09.93,0:05:11.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们被设计为便于征服其他世界的!\N{\rENG}designed to conquer other worlds! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:11.84,0:05:13.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们的身体形态会自动根据\N{\rENG}Our physical forms adjust automatically
Dialogue: 100,0:05:13.68,0:05:15.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}任何星球的重力进行调整!\N{\rENG}to the gravity of any planetoid! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:15.91,0:05:17.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 真矬!\N{\rENG}Aw, lame! 
Dialogue: 200,0:05:18.00,0:05:20.26,Song Lyrics Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_LYC}我有天在月球瞎蹦\N{\rENG_LYC}♪ I was bouncing on the moon one day ♪
Dialogue: 600,0:05:18.00,0:05:20.26,Hint,,0,0,0,,此处曲调源自"Fountain in the Park"\N与尤金·塞尔南和哈里森·施密特1972年阿波罗17号舱外活动中所唱的类似
Dialogue: 100,0:05:22.40,0:05:22.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃?\N{\rENG}Huh? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:23.22,0:05:25.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 橄榄石 那应该是谁?\N{\rENG}Hey, Peridot, who is this supposed to be? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:27.57,0:05:29.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那是蓝钻石!\N{\rENG}It's blue diamond! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:29.68,0:05:31.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等 她们都在这里?\N{\rENG}Wait. Are they all here? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:31.82,0:05:32.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊 对!\N{\rENG}Ah, yes! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:32.84,0:05:33.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她在那!\N{\rENG}There she is! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:34.04,0:05:34.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谁?\N{\rENG}Who? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:36.37,0:05:40.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}请看 黄钻石!\N{\rENG}Behold, yellow diamond! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:40.33,0:05:41.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她很雄伟吧?\N{\rENG}Isn't she magnificent? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:41.98,0:05:43.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔!\N{\rENG}Wow! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:43.60,0:05:46.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么 钻石是什么?\N{\rENG}So, who are the diamonds anyway? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:46.48,0:05:47.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们看起来很重要!\N{\rENG}They seem like a big deal! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:48.02,0:05:49.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你在开玩笑吗?\N{\rENG}Are you joking me? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:49.39,0:05:51.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}钻石是宝石人们的母亲!\N{\rENG}The diamonds are the gem matriarchs! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:51.53,0:05:53.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们一起组成了伟大的钻石政权\N{\rENG}Together they make up the great diamond authority
Dialogue: 100,0:05:53.73,0:05:56.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}掌管着母世界与所有偏远的殖民地!\N{\rENG}that governs homeworld and all the outlying colonies! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:56.76,0:05:58.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们只为服务她们!\N{\rENG}We live to serve them! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:01.82,0:06:04.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我-我指 我们最初的目的是服务她们\N{\rENG}I--I mean, we were all made to serve them
Dialogue: 100,0:06:04.33,0:06:07.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}只是一部分人不再如此\N{\rENG}even though some of us don't anymore. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:08.24,0:06:10.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 我觉得那是控制界面!\N{\rENG}Hey, I think that's a control surface over there! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:10.53,0:06:11.39,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们看看吧!\N{\rENG}Let's take a look! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:11.39,0:06:12.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好啊!\N{\rENG}Yeah! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:13.64,0:06:14.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我感觉这样才对\N{\rENG}I think this is right. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:15.20,0:06:17.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这里的材料与周围的石头不同\N{\rENG}The material is different from the surrounding stone. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:17.91,0:06:20.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我感觉如果我...这么做!\N{\rENG}I think if I just do...This! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:31.86,0:06:33.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这真是太神奇了!\N{\rENG}This is so incredible! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:33.66,0:06:36.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}只有精英中的精英才能深入这里\N{\rENG}Only the most elite of the elite can enter these sanctums. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:36.60,0:06:39.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们真的是在沿着钻石们的足迹!\N{\rENG}We are literally walking in the footsteps of the diamonds. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:39.93,0:06:41.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们肯定非常喜欢台阶\N{\rENG}They must really like stairs. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:44.91,0:06:46.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 这是什么房间?\N{\rENG}Hey, what's this room? 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:47.38,0:06:48.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这不是我们此行的目的\N{\rENG}It's not what we came for. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.24,0:06:52.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们能快点吗? 这地方让我不爽\N{\rENG}Can we hurry it up? This place gives me the creeps. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:59.08,0:07:01.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们真的在月球上了!\N{\rENG}We really are on the moon! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:01.64,0:07:02.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 我的天哪!\N{\rENG}Oh, my goodness! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:02.73,0:07:04.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这看起来还是全新的!\N{\rENG}This looks like it could be brand-new! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:04.63,0:07:06.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我是指 按现在的标准这是古董 \N{\rENG}I mean, it's a relic by today's standards, 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:06.71,0:07:08.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但 妈呀 这真是如此优雅 \N{\rENG}but, golly, it's so elegant, 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:08.68,0:07:10.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如此简洁 如此完美!\N{\rENG}so simple, so perfect! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:10.83,0:07:11.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么 你能打开它吗?\N{\rENG}So, how do you turn it on? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:12.93,0:07:14.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不会\N{\rENG}I have no idea. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:15.02,0:07:17.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 这有个发光的手形界面哎!\N{\rENG}Hey, it's got one of those glowy hand dealies! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:17.66,0:07:18.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你不能坐在那里!\N{\rENG}You can't sit there! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:18.88,0:07:20.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为什么不? 这真的很酷!\N{\rENG}Why not? It's really cool! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:20.91,0:07:23.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那个椅子只为了给最尊贵的宝石人!\N{\rENG}That chair is only for the most elite gems! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:23.53,0:07:25.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你不能随便坐到精英该坐的地方!\N{\rENG}You can't go around sitting where an elite would sit! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:25.95,0:07:28.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不过 她们现在不在 对吧?\N{\rENG}Well, they aren't here now, right? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:35.24,0:07:37.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 这个玩意是做什么的?\N{\rENG}Hey, what's this doodad for? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:37.37,0:07:38.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}把它放回去!\N{\rENG}Put that back! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:38.80,0:07:40.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗯 好吧 我们看看\N{\rENG}Hmm, okay, let's see here. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:41.22,0:07:42.03,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}开始吧\N{\rENG}There we go. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是个非常古老的系统\N{\rENG}This is a really old system. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:44.37,0:07:48.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}得找到正确的文件...\N{\rENG}Gotta find the right file...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:48.75,0:07:49.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊哈!\N{\rENG}Aha! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:49.84,0:07:52.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}融合簇 融合簇 你在哪里 融合簇?\N{\rENG}Cluster, cluster, where are you, cluster? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:52.97,0:07:53.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊哈!\N{\rENG}Aha! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这里是注入点!\N{\rENG}There's the insertion point! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:55.02,0:07:57.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看来是在切面九的第二幼儿园\N{\rENG}Looks like the beta kindergarten in facet nine. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:57.91,0:07:59.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那是两个中较小的那个 \N{\rENG}It's the smaller of the two, 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:59.13,0:08:01.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一点不如你出生的那个出色 紫晶!\N{\rENG}not nearly as impressive as yours, Amethyst! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:01.93,0:08:03.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 谢谢?\N{\rENG}Uh, thanks? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:03.88,0:08:05.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但融合簇现在在哪呢?\N{\rENG}But where is the cluster now? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:06.04,0:08:06.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等下\N{\rENG}Hang on. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.95,0:08:08.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}它在那!\N{\rENG}There it is! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}它深深的嵌入了地幔之中\N{\rENG}It's embedded deep in the mantle. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:10.60,0:08:13.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}相对于谷仓 它大概2500单位深\N{\rENG}Relative to the barn, it's roughly 2, 500 units down. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:14.06,0:08:16.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们需要做的就是将数据输入钻头 \N{\rENG}All we need to do is feed this data to the drill, 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.17,0:08:17.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}然后就可以出发了!\N{\rENG}and we should be all set! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:17.80,0:08:18.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么就这样吧!\N{\rENG}That's it, then! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:18.87,0:08:20.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}任务完成!\N{\rENG}Mission accomplished! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:20.13,0:08:21.47,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好的 团队!\N{\rENG}Yeah, team! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:21.47,0:08:22.54,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}太好了\N{\rENG}Great. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:22.54,0:08:24.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}让我们赶快离开这里吧!\N{\rENG}Let's get the heck out of here! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:24.40,0:08:25.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等 别走!\N{\rENG}Wait. Hold on! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:25.66,0:08:27.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这东西上有游戏吗?\N{\rENG}Does this thing have any games on it? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:27.57,0:08:28.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不 不 不 不\N{\rENG}No, no, no, no. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:28.46,0:08:30.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这不是用来玩的\N{\rENG}This wasn't used for games. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:30.44,0:08:30.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}唉\N{\rENG}Aw. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.15,0:08:32.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}它之前被用于规划殖民地\N{\rENG}It was used for planning the colony. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:33.00,0:08:34.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这里 看!\N{\rENG}Here, look! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:35.86,0:08:37.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是所有建造在\N{\rENG}So here's a map of all structures
Dialogue: 100,0:08:37.35,0:08:38.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}地球上的建筑的分布图\N{\rENG}that were originally built on earth. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:39.37,0:08:41.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}说实话 这可能只占\N{\rENG}All told, this probably only accounts
Dialogue: 100,0:08:41.46,0:08:43.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}原本规划的数量的5%\N{\rENG}for maybe 5% of what was originally planned! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:44.31,0:08:45.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}原来的计划是什么?\N{\rENG}What was the plan? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:45.73,0:08:47.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么 让我们看一看\N{\rENG}Well, let's take a look. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:55.17,0:08:56.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一个建成的地球殖民地!\N{\rENG}A finished earth colony! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:57.64,0:08:59.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔! 看这个!\N{\rENG}Wow! Look at this! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.35,0:09:02.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}89个幼儿园 67座尖塔 每个切面一座星际传送台\N{\rENG}89 kindergartens, 67 spires, a galaxy warp in each facet, 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:03.13,0:09:05.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有效利用一切可用资源\N{\rENG}efficient use of all available materials. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们怎么想的 要停止这个计划?\N{\rENG}What were you thinking shutting this operation down! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:07.95,0:09:09.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这本可以很伟大的!\N{\rENG}It could have been great! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:09.42,0:09:11.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不 你错了!\N{\rENG}No, you're wrong! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:11.35,0:09:12.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你什么意思?\N{\rENG}What do you mean? 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这多完美 看!\N{\rENG}It's perfect. Look at it! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:14.37,0:09:16.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们就在看啊\N{\rENG}We are looking at it. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:16.77,0:09:18.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对 这个计划太臭了!\N{\rENG}Yeah, this plan stinks! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:18.62,0:09:20.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}完成这个殖民地意味着\N{\rENG}Completing this colony would have meant
Dialogue: 100,0:09:20.15,0:09:22.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}地球生命的灭绝\N{\rENG}the extinction of all life on earth. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:22.77,0:09:24.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但想想它带来的好处-\N{\rENG}But think of the good it would have done--
Dialogue: 100,0:09:24.97,0:09:26.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}本可制造出的宝石人 \N{\rENG}the gems would that would have been made, 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:26.73,0:09:28.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们帝国的扩张!\N{\rENG}our empire expanded! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:28.61,0:09:31.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}玫瑰石英相信所有的生命都非常宝贵\N{\rENG}Rose Quartz believed all life was precious
Dialogue: 100,0:09:31.48,0:09:33.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}且值得保护!\N{\rENG}and worth protecting! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:33.68,0:09:35.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么 如果她想保护 \N{\rENG}Well, if she wanted to protect it, 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:35.02,0:09:36.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那可算是个糟糕的结局啊!\N{\rENG}she did a lousy job! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:36.95,0:09:39.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果地球还是个殖民地就不会有融合簇了!\N{\rENG}There'd be no cluster if the earth had stayed a colony! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.86,0:09:42.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在殖民地消失了 地球也不会存来了!\N{\rENG}Now there's no colony, and there's gonna be no earth! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:42.97,0:09:46.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}真感谢你 玫瑰石英-你毁了这个星球!\N{\rENG}So thank you, Rose Quartz--you doomed the planet! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:49.62,0:09:50.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦!\N{\rENG}Oh! 
Dialogue: 200,0:09:51.24,0:09:53.15,Song Lyrics Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_LYC}有什么能够比得上-\N{\rENG_LYC}♪ Is there anything that's worth more than--♪
Dialogue: 100,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你给我听着\N{\rENG}You listen to me now. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:57.31,0:10:00.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你在谈论一些你丝毫不理解的事情\N{\rENG}You are talking about things that you do not understand. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:00.80,0:10:02.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}石榴 住手 求你了!\N{\rENG}Garnet, stop, please! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:03.55,0:10:04.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这不值得\N{\rENG}It's not worth it. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:04.97,0:10:05.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}任务完成了\N{\rENG}We're done here. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:05.75,0:10:07.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}让我们回家吧\N{\rENG}Let's just go home. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:15.17,0:10:16.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我说什么了?\N{\rENG}What'd I say?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我只不过在陈述事实而已!\N{\rENG}I'm just stating a fact! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:18.20,0:10:21.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}叛乱并没有真正拯救地球\N{\rENG}The rebellion didn't really save earth. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:21.17,0:10:22.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那只是推迟了不可避免的结局而已\N{\rENG}It just delayed the inevitable. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们不是这么看的\N{\rENG}That's not the way they see it. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:25.37,0:10:27.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们花了几千年时间\N{\rENG}They've spent thousands of years
Dialogue: 100,0:10:27.02,0:10:28.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}试着保护地球\N{\rENG}trying to protect the earth. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:28.82,0:10:31.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我以为也许你最终能理解原因的\N{\rENG}I thought maybe you finally understood why. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.51,0:10:39.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}橄榄石!\N{\rENG}Peridot! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:39.77,0:10:41.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}干嘛? 我来了\N{\rENG}What? I'm coming. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:45.80,0:10:46.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}赶紧的 你们两个\N{\rENG}Let's go, you two. 

